43
0:02:18.967,000 --> 0:02:19,000
craftsmen,

44
0:02:20.142,000 --> 0:02:21,000
musicians

45
0:02:21.317,000 --> 0:02:22,000
and artists.

46
0:02:22.624,000 --> 0:02:25,000
