66
0:03:16.013,000 --> 0:03:17,000
by those trapped inside.

67
0:03:19.046,000 --> 0:03:2,000
But I've come to the stark realization

68
0:03:20.993,000 --> 0:03:21,000
that prison --

69
0:03:22.78,000 --> 0:03:23,000
