77
0:03:42.89,000 --> 0:03:43,000
And just because you're free,

78
0:03:44.673,000 --> 0:03:45,000
doesn't mean that you have freedom.

79
0:03:46.996,000 --> 0:03:49,000
Many of us, for years, have been battling our inner demons.

80
0:03:50.266,000 --> 0:03:53,000
We walk around smiling when inside we're really screamin':

81
0:03:53.631,000 --> 0:03:54,000
freedom!

82
0:03:56.171,000 --> 0:03:57,000
Don't you get it?

83
0:03:58.018,000 --> 0:03:59,000
We're all serving time;

84
0:03:59.527,000 --> 0:04:,000
