85
0:04:01.78,000 --> 0:04:02,000
As for me,

86
0:04:02.955,000 --> 0:04:04,000
I choose to be free from the prisons I've created.

87
0:04:05.559,000 --> 0:04:06,000
The key:

88
0:04:06.734,000 --> 0:04:07,000
forgiveness.

89
0:04:07.909,000 --> 0:04:08,000
Action's my witness.

90
0:04:09.084,000 --> 0:04:1,000
If we want freedom,

91
0:04:11.122,000 --> 0:04:12,000
